Package org.infernalstudios.config.annotation

Annotation Interface ListValue

@Target(FIELD) @Retention(RUNTIME) public @interface ListValue
Specifies that the field is a List field with elements that require special (de)serialization handlers. Must specify `deserialize` and `serialize` handlers. Incompatible with any possible AutoSerializable annotation used for list element class, as this annotation will take precedence.

  • Required Element Summary

    Required Elements
    Modifier and Type
    Required Element
    Description
    String
    deserialize
    The handler for deserializing the list.
    String
    serialize
    The handler for serializing the list.

  • Element Details

    • deserialize

      String deserialize
      The handler for deserializing the list. Handler must have a return type of the element in list, must accept an Object type, and must be static.

    • serialize

      String serialize
      The handler for serializing the list. Handler must have a return type of any TOML serializable value, must accept the element in list as a parameter, and must be static.
